Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:31.97,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I fall in love with him because I think he's great?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:38.40,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want you to think I'm lively, or fair, or whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.36,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\frz359.3\frx0\fry2\pos(690,381)\c&HA586A7&}10 {\c&HCBD8CF&}days until the \N{\c&H98CDC4&}School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:26.29,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I walk through the white pages of my storybook
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.08,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,just waiting to be painted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.56,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,with a kaleidoscope of my experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:39.76,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,This story has only
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.13,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,just barely begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.97,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:55.17,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wind wraps around me and urges me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:07:01.60,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand is so warm held within mine;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:08.45,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,it reaches all the way to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:15.63,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see a brighter future
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:19.93,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,than you smiling and taking my hand as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.35,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\frz359.3\frx0\fry2\pos(690,381)\c&HA586A7&}5 {\c&HCBD8CF&}days until the \N{\c&H98CDC4&}School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.65,Default,,0100,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an7\c&H7B67C0&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Happy {\c&H20CAD1&}Birthday {\c&H7B67C0&}Chizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:50.76,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly realize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.65,Default,,0000,0100,0000,,{\fs40\an9\c&H7DE4DE&}School Festival {\c&HFFFFFF&}in {\c&HCBBEF1&}3 {\c&HFFFFFF&}days!! {\c&H7DE4DE&}Last push!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.40,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,how deep my whirlpool of hidden emotions is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.86,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:06.03,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wind now says it can't wait any longer and runs ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:12.65,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories play before my eyes like a revolving lantern,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:19.42,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,endlessly, innocently, and oh so brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:26.62,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,My fear, my weaknesses, all transform into the high-flying wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.40,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:36.20,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand is warmer and gentler than any other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:43.14,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,and it reaches all the way to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:50.30,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll smile and take my hand as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.55,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll never let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.74,Fortune,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H050A09&\pos(537,167)\frz5.081}Excellent Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:40.44,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I fall in love with Kazehaya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:56.49,Default,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleased to announce the beginning of \Nthe 43rd Kitahoro High School Festival! {looks so amazing}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:56.49,Festival,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,260)}43rd Kitahoro High School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Café this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come see the Astronomy Club's planetarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.74,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We have fortune telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Cult fortune telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs40\fnBrianne's hand\c&H0C130C&\3c&HF0F4F5&}Sadako's Black Magic Cafe\N{\fs25}[Mystery] Black Magic Consultations Happening Now [Dark Arts]\N{\fs35}- Herbal Teas - Herbal Sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The guy I like has a girlfriend and I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:45.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything to make him mine and make his girlfriend fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:51.58,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's said that to curse someone is to curse yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:58.30,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that you may end up causing \Nyourself harm as well, so I suggest… {if it were me…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.40,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:04.27,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with this evil aura?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.43,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors about Kuronuma set off more rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:10.89,Ryu's Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(514,572)\3c&H8D4B9B&}Sadako's Black Magic Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.89,Ryu's Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz356.096\pos(720,124)}End of the Line
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:10.89,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,and a bunch of people who want to cast black magic showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.77,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,This is because of her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.17,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best to compete with his girlfriend fairly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hate her even if I lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:26.42,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, they all leave cured of their malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.04,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Next guest, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:36.25,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry, we don't play "super cute rock-paper-scissors" here. {this is americanization and it's evil.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.96,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your Perilla tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What is this tea good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's effective against constipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.91,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Chigusa! It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:53.00,Default,Chigusa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so do you have herbal ramen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.06,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:58.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:04.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magic Café is going on a ten minute break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:19.18,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person she likes has a girlfriend…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:22.77,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are more love troubles than anything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:36.67,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Kazehaya didn't like someone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.92,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was there something I could've done?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:44.45,Fortune 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\be1\blur5\frz9.625\move(251,516,217,349,0,5860)}Love\NDedication to love\N will bring happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:44.45,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would things be different now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They wouldn't, would they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.68,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako! {GO AWAY ><}\NGood work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.09,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I brought this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.23,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I was Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:08.44,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane will give me hell for interfering \Nagain, but I just can't leave this alone. {THEN GO AWAY}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.27,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Can I tell you what I really think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:19.69,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was impossible to make Kazehaya fall for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:27.88,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you two were too \Ndifferent and wouldn't make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:32.11,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if Kazehaya actually \Nfell for someone, it wouldn't be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:41.05,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,And even though you said that you don't feel a wall between you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.80,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I see a wall between you and him and no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.43,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,A wall that you don't have with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.89,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only with Kazehaya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.21,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:02.87,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But you're actually pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:11.06,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought you should give up on Kazehaya, try \Nto fit in with the class, and choose someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.79,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Along that line of thought, I figured why not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.51,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.89,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I think you look much better when you're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.20,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess now, the only one who can make you upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.81,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,make you cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.42,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,and make you laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.06,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,is Kazehaya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.95,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.24,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:54.63,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A wall with Kazehaya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:59.63,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feeling embarrassed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:26.50,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not wanting him to hate me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.86,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}being unable to laugh normally,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.17,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}unable to say what's on my mind…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:38.60,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did I create this wall{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}between the two of us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:49.66,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I said what I really thought, Kazehaya \Nalways answered me with full honesty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.22,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.22,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:16:01.14,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako… It's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.23,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.20,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:09.35,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think Kuronuma has the wrong idea about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:09.86,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:17.89,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But I think Kuronuma has had to deal with people \Nhaving the wrong idea about her for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.83,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she's never given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:26.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm the exact opposite of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.87,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,quick to get angry, with a jealous streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:33.86,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not the amazing person she thinks I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:38.85,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,and definitely not someone worth admiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:44.35,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma always says "It's all thanks to you, Kazehaya!",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,but she's always trying her best all on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.07,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,always trying to make things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:55.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who admires her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We came to check out your Black Magic Café!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:12.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard it really works!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That Sadako Kuronuma is a natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:17.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.93,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sawako Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.90,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought he was like a god.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:58.05,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bright, lively, and always the center of attention.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magic Café was a great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:03.30,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I respected him, admired him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:13.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but when did he change from a god to just an ordinary guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.78,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.16,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.95,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,The costume parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.58,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It might take all night to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.94,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.33,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:34.24,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, eat, take a bath, then come meet up at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.71,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you seen Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.94,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.68,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you can't find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.65,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.02,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.59,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.02,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.74,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,who Kazehaya likes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.66,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Go on without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.46,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, he's in the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those things don't matter anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.95,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to for you to let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.33,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if things are scary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.93,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if I'm embarrassed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.88,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or what he thinks of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.58,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why was I hesitating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:55.21,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are so many things I want to say to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.88,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.96,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how he looks when he blushes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.88,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he's anxious,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.77,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he's angry,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.77,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he's serious,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.42,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he's sad,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he has a big sparkling smile on his face…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:19.50,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I told him I wanted all of that,{\i0}
